Program: Discovery
Title: Music and Memory
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrx8m
Last Broadcast Date: 07 December 1998
How music can help us explore the human mind A journey deep inside the brain in Montreal, Canada, to examine the effect of music on memory. Also in the programme how the blind can see; exciting new treatments for diseases like epilepsy and multiple sclerosis.